    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Applicant
    Represents an applicant in the Build-To-Order system.
    ApplicantCLI
    CLI class for Applicants to interact with BTO project application features.
    Application
    Represents a BTO application submitted by an applicant for a specific project and flat type.
    Application.Status
    Represents the status of an application throughout the BTO process.
    ApplicationCLI
    Handles the applicant's interaction with BTO project applications.
    ApplicationController
    Handles application-related logic such as submission, withdrawal, filtering, and processing for both applicants, managers, and officers.
    ApplicationManagementCLI
    CLI interface for managing BTO applications.
    ApplicationRegistry
    Central registry for storing and retrieving BTO applications by applicants.
    AuthController
    Controller responsible for user authentication and account management.
    Breadcrumb
    Utility for tracking user navigation paths within the CLI system.
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant regarding a specific BTO project.
    EnquiryCLI
    CLI for managing enquiries submitted by applicants or viewed by HDB staff.
    EnquiryController
    Handles the submission, retrieval, editing, and replying of enquiries made by users.
    EnquiryRegistry
    Registry for storing and retrieving all enquiries submitted by applicants.
    ExcelReader
    Utility for reading user, project, application, and enquiry data from an Excel file.
    ExcelReader.ExcelData
     
    ExcelWriter
    Utility for saving user credentials, applications, projects, and enquiries into an Excel file for persistence.
    Filter
    Represents a reusable set of filter criteria for searching and listing projects or applications based on flat type, price, age, marital status, etc.
    FilterUtil
    Utility for applying a Filter object to a list of ISearchable items.
    FlatType
    Represents a flat type available in a BTO project.
    HDBManager
    Represents a manager in the Build-To-Order system.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents an HDB Officer in the Build-To-Order system.
    HDBOfficer.RegistrationStatus
    Represents the registration status of an HDB officer.
    InputUtil
    Utility for safely reading typed input from the console, such as integers.
    ISearchable
    Interface implemented by classes that support filter-based searching.
    LoginCLI
    Handles the login interface for users in the Build-To-Order Management System.
    MainApp
    Entry point of the BTO application system.
    ManagerCLI
    CLI interface for HDB Managers.
    ManagerController
    Controller responsible for all project-related operations by HDB managers, including project creation, configuration, officer approvals, and more.
    OfficerCLI
    CLI interface for HDB Officers in the Build-To-Order Management System.
    OfficerController
    Controller for handling actions available to HDB Officers, including project registration, registration status checks, project viewing, flat assignment, and receipt generation.
    Project
    Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) housing project.
    ProjectManagementCLI
    CLI interface for HDB Managers to create, view, and manage BTO projects.
    ProjectRegistry
    Registry for storing and retrieving BTO projects by name.
    TableUtil
    Utility for rendering formatted CLI tables with pagination support.
    User
    Abstract base class representing a user in the Build-To-Order system.
